\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 As they hung out, the faint sound of a bell echoed in the distance, cutting through the laughter and chatter. One of the boys\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 a tall, lanky kid with a mischievous grin\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 shouted, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93It\u8217\'92s the class bell! Let\u8217\'92s go!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 The others scrambled into action, quickly packing up their baseball gear and rushing toward their motorcycles. Nagano slung his glove over his shoulder and jogged toward his bike, his movements quick and practiced.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93C\u8217\'92mon, let\u8217\'92s go! The class is starting!\u8221\'94 Sakura called, already running toward one of the motorcycles. Haruki hesitated for a moment, then followed, her heart pounding as she tried to keep up.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Sakura hopped onto the seat behind one of the boys, her arms wrapping around his waist as the engine roared to life. The other boys followed suit, their motorcycles growling like restless beasts.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Hey! Haruki!\u8221\'94 Nagano\u8217\'92s voice cut through the noise, and she turned to see him sitting on his motorcycle, his helmet already on. He grinned at her, patting the seat behind him. \u8220\'93C\u8217\'92mon, you don\u8217\'92t want to be late on your first day at Fukumitsu, do you?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Haruki stared at him for a moment, her mind racing. This was surreal. She was about to ride a motorcycle with her father\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 her\~}{\f0\fs24\b0\i1 young}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~father\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 to a school that existed decades before she was born. But there was no time to think. The other motorcycles were already pulling away, their engines roaring as they sped down the road.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 She took a deep breath and ran toward Nagano, hopping onto the seat behind him. Her arms instinctively wrapped around his waist as he revved the engine, the vibrations coursing through her.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Hold on tight!\u8221\'94 he called over his shoulder, his voice barely audible over the noise. Before she could respond, he hit the throttle, and the motorcycle surged forward.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 The wind whipped through Haruki\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s hair as they sped down the road, the world blurring around her. She clung to Nagano, her heart racing as they weaved through the streets. The other motorcycles were ahead of them, their riders laughing and shouting as they raced toward the school.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Haruki\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s mind was a whirlwind of emotions\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 fear, excitement, disbelief. She was riding through 1960s Japan on a motorcycle with her father, heading to a school that shouldn\u8217\'92t exist in this time. It was like something out of a dream, but the feel of the wind on her face and the rumble of the engine beneath her told her it was real.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 As they approached the school, Nagano slowed down, pulling into the parking lot alongside the others. He cut the engine and turned to Haruki, his grin wide and carefree. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Not bad for your first ride, huh?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Haruki nodded, her legs trembling slightly as she climbed off the motorcycle. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Yeah\u8230\'85 not bad.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Nagano laughed, slinging his bag over his shoulder. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93C\u8217\'92mon, let\u8217\'92s get to class. You don\u8217\'92t want to miss your first day.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Haruki followed him, her mind still reeling. She didn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t know what to expect, but one thing was clear: this was just the beginning. She was in the past, surrounded by people who would one day shape her future. And she had no idea what to do next.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 But for now, all she could do was follow Nagano, her heart pounding with a mix of fear and determination.}}